       Hell Beast and his team assemble a mile southwest of what used to be 
the Cybertronian Fire. With the rally point set into the Neo Decepticon's 
radar, Hell Beast contacts the leader.
       "Unicron, we are lagging behinde from the CF assault. It would be 
greatly appreciated if you were to deliver a new set of orders and 
coordinates for us." He said, "Preferably a place where we can reload and get 
repairs. Hell Beast over and out."
       He switched off the comminication and looked at his men. Ragged, 
tired, beaten, but not broken. There was a victory in that battle, for Hell 
Beasts men at least. And that would keep them strong.

--part1_8f.a3d12c8.2821b3bf_boundary
